  "description": "Delicate high-register texture that flickers. LFO2 on drama creates subtle coupling oscillation — partials drift toward synchrony then scatter, like moths circling a lamp. Bright tilt, low partial count, high resonance sensitivity means small clusters flash into existence and vanish. Fragile and hypnotic.",
